TITLE PlaneWeightsShard2026v1
VERSION 1
CATEGORY ECOSAFETY

SUMMARY
Plane weights and non-offsettable flags for ecosafety Lyapunov residual.

fields
  contractid      string   # e.g. PhoenixEcosafetyContinuity2026v1
  planeid         string   # e.g. energy, hydrologyMAR, biodiversity, carbon
  weight          f32      # w_j >= 0
  nonoffsettable  bool     # true means plane cannot be offset by other planes
  softband        f32      # soft corridor band for r_j
  hardband        f32      # hard corridor band for r_j
  uncertaintycap  f32      # max tolerated uncertainty on r_j
  versiontag      string   # PlaneWeightsShard2026v1
  proofrefhex     string   # hex link to ecosafety proof bundle

